edu.ncsu.csc.Galant.prefs

Class Preference<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.Galant.prefs.Preference<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of the value.

    public class Preference<V>
extends java.lang.Object

    A representation of a user preference. It's essentially just a container for a value, which can be pushed to a persistent backing store via a Preferences node. Calling store() pushes the main value to the backing store. When the Preference object is created, it gets its inital value from the backing store if available.
